Moderators, Editors and Subtitlers. 💞

250
00:17:33,680 --> 00:17:38,119
Baby, do you plan to marry Ding Ran?

251
00:17:43,239 --> 00:17:48,100
You don't need to be so surprised. There were some signs, anyway.

252
00:17:48,100 --> 00:17:51,620
Besides, Ding Ran's disguise was not very good.

253
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:55,120
It was me.

254
00:17:55,120 --> 00:17:58,040
I didn't want you to find out, so I dragged him away.

255
00:17:58,040 --> 00:18:00,239
Baby.

256
00:18:00,239 --> 00:18:01,999
I'm sorry.

257
00:18:01,999 --> 00:18:07,460
Are you afraid that after I find out about your relationship, I'll give up on marrying Uncle Ding?

258
00:18:12,820 --> 00:18:14,899
That's what she thought.

259
00:18:14,899 --> 00:18:19,559
So we wanted to wait until after you got married, then we would tell you the truth.

260
00:18:19,559 --> 00:18:21,480
Silly kids.

261
00:18:21,480 --> 00:18:24,999
So, do you plan to get married?

262
00:18:26,580 --> 00:18:29,799
I... I...

263
00:18:32,839 --> 00:18:34,040
Yes.

264
00:18:34,040 --> 00:18:35,699
Auntie Baobei,

265
00:18:36,420 --> 00:18:38,859
I've liked your daughter

266
00:18:39,560 --> 00:18:42,119
for a very, very long time.

267
00:18:42,119 --> 00:18:44,220
I want to marry her.

268
00:18:44,220 --> 00:18:46,300
I want to live with her.

269
00:18:47,339 --> 00:18:51,580
I want to say to her every day when I leave, "I'm going to work."

270
00:18:51,580 --> 00:18:57,679
When I come home every day, I want to say to her, "I'm back."

271
00:18:59,199 --> 00:19:02,119
What about you, Xile?

272
00:19:02,119 --> 00:19:04,059
I…

273
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:08,310
Mom.

274
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:13,680
From when I was in school, I've always liked one person, and that's Ding Ran.

275
00:19:16,440 --> 00:19:20,420
It's been ten years. I've never liked

276
00:19:20,420 --> 00:19:22,839
anyone else but him.

277
00:19:24,239 --> 00:19:27,520
In that case, your Uncle Ding and I have an idea.

278
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:29,960
I don't know if you'll feel it's too casual.

279
00:19:29,960 --> 00:19:32,660
Mom, you absolutely can't sacrifice yourselves for us.

280
00:19:32,660 --> 00:19:34,219
We wouldn't be happy that way.

281
00:19:34,219 --> 00:19:36,720
That's right, Auntie Baobei, you and my Dad should live well first.

282
00:19:36,720 --> 00:19:39,079
We can talk about us later.

283
00:19:39,079 --> 00:19:43,720
We... We don't want to sacrifice ourselves for you.

284
00:19:43,720 --> 00:19:47,499
What we mean is, if you two also decide to get married,

285
00:19:49,339 --> 00:19:51,500
why don't we marry together?

286
00:19:52,119 --> 00:19:54,919
Marry together?

287
00:20:05,761 --> 00:20:11,672
♫ I look at you from behind ♫

288
00:20:14,159 --> 00:20:16,260
Silly look.

289
00:20:17,620 --> 00:20:19,259
All right, stop being silly.

290
00:20:19,259 --> 00:20:21,679
- Hurry up and eat, then go to work early.
- Okay.

291
00:20:21,679 --> 00:20:24,928
Okay.

292
00:20:24,928 --> 00:20:30,610
♫ I rely on you outside of your world ♫

293
00:20:32,380 --> 00:20:39,100
♫ You are the love that's out of reach ♫

294
00:20:39,100 --> 00:20:44,913
♫ But I'm waiting like a child ♫

295
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:49,980
Our family is open and loving.

296
00:20:49,980 --> 00:20:52,039
We're going to get married together.

297
00:20:52,039 --> 00:20:56,899
If anyone dares to gossip, I'll make her pay a gift first.

298
00:20:56,899 --> 00:20:58,219
I think it will do.

299
00:20:58,219 --> 00:21:01,700
Qi Fei told me there would be a good date next month.

300
00:21:02,540 --> 00:21:06,320
Ding Ran, are you serious or joking?

301
00:21:06,320 --> 00:21:08,240
Baby, change your clothes.

302
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:10,520
Let's go to the wedding shop to pick a dress.

303
00:21:10,520 --> 00:21:14,099
- Mom, isn't this too urgent?
- Let's go.

304
00:21:14,760 --> 00:21:16,184
Go.

305
00:21:18,639 --> 00:21:23,580
♫ Grant me the chance to no longer face the crowd ♫

306
00:21:23,580 --> 00:21:26,480
♫ How did I meet you? ♫

307
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:27,980
Go on eating.

308
00:21:27,980 --> 00:21:29,479
Okay.

309
00:21:30,919 --> 00:21:34,870
Tomorrow is a holiday. Remember to pick a suit.

310
00:21:34,870 --> 00:21:38,250
♫ Even if the sea in the palm of my hand is empty, I will not let go ♫

311
00:21:38,250 --> 00:21:45,296
♫ Even if the storm comes again, I don't want to hide ♫

312
00:21:45,296 --> 00:21:50,839
♫ Under your eaves, we meet without feeling like strangers now ♫

313
00:21:50,839 --> 00:21:54,540
You brat, congratulations.

314
00:21:56,839 --> 00:21:59,019
Be good to Xile.

315
00:21:59,019 --> 00:22:00,608
I will.

316
00:22:07,900 --> 00:22:09,900
Dad, have a fried egg.

317
00:22:09,900 --> 00:22:11,360
Okay.

318
00:22:11,360 --> 00:22:15,100
♫ You are the love that's out of reach ♫

319
00:22:16,500 --> 00:22:20,300
Baby, you can use the money on this card as you wish.

320
00:22:20,300 --> 00:22:23,300
Mom, why are you giving me money?

321
00:22:24,700 --> 00:22:26,800
Whether it's your career

322
00:22:26,800 --> 00:22:30,600
or your dating and marriage, you will need money.

323
00:22:30,600 --> 00:22:35,200
Even though the Ding family doesn't lack money, I don't want you to use others' money.

324
00:22:35,200 --> 00:22:37,700
I still want to keep this face.

325
00:22:37,700 --> 00:22:39,400
Take it.

326
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:44,100
Mom, how can I accept this?

327
00:22:45,900 --> 00:22:49,000
Do you know why I want to hold the wedding with you?

328
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:50,400
Why?

329
00:22:50,400 --> 00:22:55,900
Because in this way, we can hold one banquet and collect two gifts.

330
00:22:55,900 --> 00:22:58,500
I'm smart, right?

331
00:22:59,600 --> 00:23:02,500
I used to care too much about what others thought.

332
00:23:02,500 --> 00:23:04,700
Actually, it's none of their business.

333
00:23:04,700 --> 00:23:11,300
So, this time, I want to tell all those gossipy relatives.

334
00:23:15,100 --> 00:23:18,300
Mom, thank you.

335
00:23:27,500 --> 00:23:30,600
Why are you so good?

336
00:23:41,600 --> 00:23:43,700
Great photo.

337
00:23:44,700 --> 00:23:47,900
Jiang Xile is finally getting married. Poor Ding Ran.

338
00:23:47,900 --> 00:23:51,500
How is he poor? Xile is so beautiful.

339
00:23:51,500 --> 00:23:54,100
- The four of us registered on the same day.
- Not just the four of us,

340
00:23:54,100 --> 00:23:57,100
- it's the six of us.
- Six?

341
00:23:57,100 --> 00:23:59,270
Including Uncle and Auntie.

342
00:23:59,270 --> 00:24:00,800
Wow.

343
00:24:00,800 --> 00:24:03,000
Come on. Here comes the cake.

344
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:05,300
Such a beautiful cake.

345
00:24:05,300 --> 00:24:07,500
Give me your marriage certificates.

346
00:24:07,500 --> 00:24:09,300
I want to take a picture and post it on Moments.

347
00:24:09,300 --> 00:24:12,000
Okay, let's show off.

348
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:15,200
By the way, Xile, where are you and Ding Ran planning to have your honeymoon?

349
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:17,500
We don't want to be too high-profile.

350
00:24:17,500 --> 00:24:21,000
- We're thinking about going back to our hometown for our honeymoon.
- Right.

351
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:24,500
Liuliu, what about you and Qi Fei? You need to pick a date soon.

352
00:24:24,500 --> 00:24:27,600
Otherwise, your wedding dress won't fit.

353
00:24:27,600 --> 00:24:30,500
I was thinking that the six of us could hold the wedding together.

354
00:24:30,500 --> 00:24:34,600
It's okay. We also welcome you to have your honeymoon in our village.

355
00:24:34,600 --> 00:24:36,400
Back to the village, sounds good.

356
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:40,300
I miss the days when the four of us spent time in the village.

357
00:24:40,300 --> 00:24:43,300
We can also check on Jiang Jiang. See if it's grown up.

358
00:24:43,300 --> 00:24:46,800
Right, we should go back and check on Jiang Jiang.

359
00:24:46,800 --> 00:24:51,500
So, that time at the hometown, it was the four of you together?

360
00:24:51,500 --> 00:24:55,400
Such a small place, three rooms for four people. How did you live?

361
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:57,200
Auntie, let me tell you about this.

362
00:24:57,200 --> 00:24:58,900
At that time, the two of them already—

363
00:24:58,900 --> 00:25:00,500
Liuliu, Liuliu.

364
00:25:00,500 --> 00:25:02,400
- Thirsty? Want some juice?
- Not thirsty.

365
00:25:02,400 --> 00:25:04,800
Stop interrupting. Liuliu, keep going, I want to hear.

366
00:25:04,800 --> 00:25:07,700
Uncle, let me tell you, at that time, the two of them…

367
00:25:07,700 --> 00:25:09,000
Qi Fei. Dad.

368
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:11,600
Dad, Mom, do you know what "have tea" means?

369
00:25:11,600 --> 00:25:14,500
Liuliu and Qi Fei started from "having tea."

370
00:25:14,500 --> 00:25:16,400
You two want to have tea? I have good tea.

371
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:17,600
No, no, Uncle.

372
00:25:17,600 --> 00:25:20,400
- Not that kind of having tea.
- I want to drink juice. Come on, let's toast.

373
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:21,700
Come on, cheers.

374
00:25:21,700 --> 00:25:22,900
Come on.

375
00:25:22,900 --> 00:25:25,100
Cheers.

376
00:25:28,100 --> 00:25:31,400
By the way, we haven't named our baby yet.

377
00:25:31,400 --> 00:25:33,600
Can you help us come up with one?

378
00:25:34,600 --> 00:25:36,700
Qi Fei.

379
00:25:36,700 --> 00:25:37,800
Liuliu.

380
00:25:37,800 --> 00:25:40,000
Qi Liuhai.

381
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:42,300
- What a terrible name!
- What kind of name is that?

382
00:25:42,300 --> 00:25:44,000
It's even crazier than my name.

383
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:47,100
Liuliu, who came up with your name? Why is it so crazy?

384
00:25:47,100 --> 00:25:50,000
I… Let's not talk about this. Let's take a picture.

385
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:52,300
Let's take a family photo.

386
00:25:52,300 --> 00:25:54,200
- You take this, take this.
- Me?

387
00:25:54,200 --> 00:25:56,400
- Hold it.
- Okay, okay.

388
00:25:56,400 --> 00:25:58,200
Hold this.

389
00:25:58,200 --> 00:25:59,800
Three, two, one.

390
00:25:59,800 --> 00:26:04,100
We're married!

391
00:26:11,000 --> 00:26:12,700
What are you doing?

392
00:26:12,700 --> 00:26:16,600
Didn't you ask me to fold your clothes when we had dinner?

393
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:20,590
Right, I'll help you.

394
00:26:20,590 --> 00:26:22,500
[Ding Ran]

395
00:26:24,900 --> 00:26:28,400
Do you remember this shirt?

396
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:34,200
[Ding Ran Xile]

397
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:36,500
The one I gave you.

398
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:39,400
You didn't throw it away?

399
00:26:39,400 --> 00:26:42,300
How could I throw away something you gave me?

400
00:26:42,300 --> 00:26:45,600
Then why did you lend it to Xu Shanshan?

401
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:49,500
It really was Xu Shanshan, she forcefully borrowed it from me.

402
00:26:51,100 --> 00:26:52,600
Okay.

403
00:26:53,600 --> 00:26:55,900
I'll call her right now.

404
00:26:58,500 --> 00:27:00,000
You still have her number?

405
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:01,900
I'll delete it right away.

406
00:27:04,600 --> 00:27:07,100
Forget it, forget it. It's just Xu Shanshan.

407
00:27:07,100 --> 00:27:09,400
I don't care about her.

408
00:27:09,400 --> 00:27:12,800
♫ Thinking back to when we first met ♫

409
00:27:12,800 --> 00:27:17,300
♫ I had sweaty palms and my senses awestruck ♫

410
00:27:17,300 --> 00:27:18,840
Delete it.

411
00:27:18,840 --> 00:27:23,700
♫ Ten years of missed opportunity, now reunited with regret ♫

412
00:27:23,700 --> 00:27:27,400
♫ All at once, overnight, I realized I had loved you deeply then ♫

413
00:27:27,400 --> 00:27:29,000
I deleted it.

414
00:27:31,500 --> 00:27:34,600
No, no, you disrupted my plan.

415
00:27:35,299 --> 00:27:38,000
- Open it and have a look.
- Look at what?

416
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:39,900
The pocket.

417
00:27:41,300 --> 00:27:44,000
♫ Missing you is hard to endure ♫

418
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:50,300
♫ You haunt my dreams, yet you completely ignore me ♫

419
00:27:50,300 --> 00:27:53,300
♫ It dawned on me overnight that after all the twists and turns, I still love you deeply ♫

420
00:27:53,300 --> 00:27:57,000
♫ It dawned on me overnight that after all the twists and turns, I still love you deeply ♫

421
00:27:57,000 --> 00:27:59,700
♫ Back then, I was oblivious, pushing you away and regrets unravel as we reunite ♫

422
00:27:59,700 --> 00:28:01,800
Wedding ring.

423
00:28:03,700 --> 00:28:07,900
♫ I want to wait until we both have white hair ♫

424
00:28:07,900 --> 00:28:09,400
I'm sorry.

425
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:12,600
We originally agreed to go back together.

426
00:28:12,600 --> 00:28:14,800
But the training time was suddenly set.

427
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:17,500
You go back first and wait for me.

428
00:28:17,500 --> 00:28:18,900
It's okay.

429
00:28:18,900 --> 00:28:22,700
When you arrive, I'll rush out to greet you.

430
00:28:22,700 --> 00:28:24,500
All right.

431
00:28:24,500 --> 00:28:25,800
Then I'll go back.

432
00:28:25,800 --> 00:28:27,700
Wait a moment.

433
00:28:27,700 --> 00:28:29,500
I bought a new mattress.

434
00:28:29,500 --> 00:28:31,600
Do you want to try it?

435
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:36,200
I don't want to try.

436
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:38,000
Why don't you want to?

437
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:42,100
What's so good about trying a mattress? Aren't they all the same?

438
00:28:42,100 --> 00:28:43,300
Not the same.

439
00:28:43,300 --> 00:28:45,100
Where's the difference?

440
00:28:45,100 --> 00:28:47,200
Everywhere is different.

441
00:28:47,900 --> 00:28:50,600
Then you try it yourself.

442
00:28:50,600 --> 00:28:52,500
How can I try it myself?

443
00:28:52,500 --> 00:28:55,300
I don't care how you try.

444
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:59,900
♫ All at once, overnight, I realized I had loved you deeply then ♫

445
00:28:59,900 --> 00:29:03,700
♫ All at once, overnight, I realized I had loved you deeply then ♫

446
00:29:03,700 --> 00:29:06,500
♫ Memories of you laughing, crying, and forgotten feelings ♫

447
00:29:06,500 --> 00:29:10,300
♫ Memories of you laughing, crying, and forgotten feelings ♫

448
00:29:10,300 --> 00:29:14,600
♫ The most intimate thoughts turned into nothingness ♫

449
00:29:14,600 --> 00:29:17,300
♫ Missing you is hard to endure ♫

450
00:29:17,300 --> 00:29:23,700
♫ You haunt my dreams, yet you completely ignore me ♫

451
00:29:23,700 --> 00:29:25,900
All right, let's try it.

452
00:29:26,600 --> 00:29:30,300
♫ It dawned on me overnight that after all the twists and turns, I still love you deeply ♫

453
00:29:30,300 --> 00:29:33,500
♫ Back then, I was oblivious, pushing you away and regrets unravel as we reunite ♫

454
00:29:33,500 --> 00:29:35,900
- I told you this mattress was good.
- It's not good at all.

455
00:29:35,900 --> 00:29:38,100
- This is not good?
- You're just a liar.

456
00:29:38,100 --> 00:29:39,700
I'm a liar?

457
00:29:39,700 --> 00:29:44,900
♫ Together we can make up for the love we missed ♫

458
00:29:46,600 --> 00:29:48,200
Slow down.

459
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:52,200
Jiang Xile, I'm pregnant, not with a broken leg.

460
00:29:52,200 --> 00:29:53,700
I can walk.

461
00:29:53,700 --> 00:29:55,700
In your womb is my goddaughter.

462
00:29:55,700 --> 00:29:58,200
I have to take good care of you.

463
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:03,100
Jiang Xile, thank you.

464
00:30:03,100 --> 00:30:09,200
In my teenage years when no one cared about me, you were always a good friend to me.

465
00:30:09,200 --> 00:30:11,000
It's so good to have you.

466
00:30:11,900 --> 00:30:15,000
I've thought about the name for your child.

467
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:18,400
Apart from Qi Liuhai, tell me.

468
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:21,400
Qi Lerongrong.

469
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:23,900
It sounds okay.

470
00:30:23,900 --> 00:30:26,000
What do you mean okay? It's very good.

471
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:29,500
It's a little better than before.

472
00:30:29,500 --> 00:30:31,800
I bought the vegetables and you two just picked up Jiang Jiang.

473
00:30:31,800 --> 00:30:33,500
You better take your wife away.

474
00:30:33,500 --> 00:30:36,300
It's okay, I'll go with you.

475
00:30:36,300 --> 00:30:41,000
Look, to satisfy your girlhood wish to ride a bicycle,

476
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:43,900
Qi Fei specially changed to ride a bicycle.

477
00:30:43,900 --> 00:30:46,400
Custom-made, won't you try it?

478
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:48,200
- Then I'll go first.
- Go ahead.

479
00:30:48,200 --> 00:30:50,200
- See you in five minutes, bye.
- Bye.

480
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:52,600
- Let's go.
- Be careful.

481
00:30:52,600 --> 00:30:54,500
Not bad, right?

482
00:30:56,100 --> 00:30:57,400
Hold on tight.

483
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:59,300
Let's go.

484
00:31:06,900 --> 00:31:09,100
Pick a small flower.

485
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:13,800
Here.

486
00:31:13,800 --> 00:31:15,900
Three, two, one.

487
00:31:18,700 --> 00:31:21,200
Jiang Jiang, you're so cute.

488
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:23,200
Have you had enough?

489
00:31:23,200 --> 00:31:25,800
Sleepy, Jiang Jiang is sleepy.

490
00:31:25,800 --> 00:31:28,300
- Have you fed it?
- Yes, it's full.

491
00:31:28,300 --> 00:31:30,700
It was just sleepy.

492
00:31:30,700 --> 00:31:33,500
- It'll be ready soon?
- Yes, it's ready.

493
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:37,400
It smells so good.

494
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:39,800
- How is it?
- It looks delicious.

495
00:31:39,800 --> 00:31:41,700
Of course.

496
00:31:41,700 --> 00:31:44,400
Do I, Chef Qi, need to say more about my cooking skills? Come on, eat.

497
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:48,000
Why do you look as if you have a load on your mind?

498
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:50,800
No, I don't. I'm so happy.

499
00:31:52,300 --> 00:31:54,000
Missing your husband?

500
00:31:54,000 --> 00:31:56,100
Why should I miss him?

501
00:31:56,700 --> 00:31:58,500
You don't really?

502
00:31:58,500 --> 00:31:59,800
No.

503
00:31:59,800 --> 00:32:02,100
Look into my eyes and say it again.

